Novo Demands Cash on Delivery for Greek Drugs, The Times Says

-- B y   B e n   F a r e y
-- 
2011-07-02T08:41:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-02/novo-demands-cash-on-delivery-for-greek-drugs-the-times-says.html
Novo Nordisk A/S is insisting it’s
paid in cash when it delivers medicines to Greek hospitals in a
move designed to limit debt,  The Times  reported, citing a
spokesman for the world’s biggest supplier of insulin.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Farey in London at 
